{"type": "article", "id": 8993, "title": "芭蕾家具", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-29T07:33:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235000GSKQpAw0rv6lIOLF.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t新西兰设计工作室 Goldsworthy 为同样来自新西兰的家具厂商设计了一个叫做 “Ballet” 的家具系列，包括一个扶手椅，一个普通椅子，和一个桌子。和其名字 “Ballet” 一样，这套家具看上去简单优雅，清新可人，材料上选用的是欧洲木复合夹板，而颜色采用渐变的蓝色，圆锥状的桌子看上去像舞者的身姿，椅子流畅的线条看上去舒适而放松。这里是<a href=\"http://www.backhousenz.com/\" target=\"_blank\"> Backhouse 的官方主页</a>，以及这是<a href=\"http://goldsworthystudio.com/\" target=\"_blank\"> Goldsworthy 的作品集</a>，感兴趣的话，可以点击查看。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234957DFGsgktxdwlSvWIK.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.6462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234958LdZeRm9DCTys8i6B.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.65\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052349589PSOkiretvTYbFfD.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.63425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234959qwjfvYhelguEmnNZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.95599022\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234959jkIJ1Zy8NFtpL7aR.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.91564792\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234959OIjMTwGH4VunfCDl.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0